    <h2 class="bold font-l">Elite X-Nauts</h2>
    <p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
      Elite X-Nauts wear red and black uniforms and defend the moon base where the evil Grodus is holding Peach.    </p>
    <p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RedAndBlackAndEvilAllOver"class='trope-example-link'>Red and Black and Evil All Over</a></p>

